?\nA strange black block is stuck to it.","words":[[47,"At"],[48,"the"],[49,"bottom"],[50,"of"],[51,"the"],[52,"drawer,"],[53,"Rinky"],[54,"finds"],[55,"his"],[56,"special"],[57,"pen."],[58,"But"],[59,"what’s"],[60,"that?"],[61,"A"],[62,"strange"],[63,"black"],[64,"block"],[65,"is"],[66,"stuck"],[67,"to"],[68,"it."]]},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55423/size6/1dc0be3b19aab62dd9720b54ae8c45b3.jpg","text":"Rinky pulls the pen and the block apart.\nBut then…\nPlink, click! \nA bottle-cap jumps and sticks to the block! Rinky giggles with delight.\nCan things stick to this block like magic?","words":[[69,"Rinky"],[70,"pulls"],[71,"the"],[72,"pen"],[73,"and"],[74,"the"],[75,"block"],[76,"apart."],[77,"But"],[78,"then…"],[79,"Plink,"],[80,"click!"],[81,"A"],[82,"bottle-cap"],[83,"jumps"],[84,"and"],[85,"sticks"],[86,"to"],[87,"the"],[88,"block!"],[89,"Rinky"],[90,"giggles"],[91,"with"],[92,"delight"],[93,"."],[94,"Can"],[95,"things"],[96,"stick"],[97,"to"],[98,"this"],[99,"block"],[100,"like"],[101,"magic?"]]},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55424/size6/16d7e2beedd74927fa3574487e21fd55.jpg","text":"Does the stapler stick to this block?\nPlink, click! Yes, it sticks.                                           \nDoes the furry cat stick to it?\nNo, it does not.","words":[[102,"Does"],[103,"the"],[104,"stapler"],[105,"stick"],[106,"to"],[107,"this"],[108,"block?"],[109,"Plink,"],[110,"click!"],[111,"Yes,"],[112,"it"],[113,"sticks."],[114,"Does"],[115,"the"],[116,"furry"],[117,"cat"],[118,"stick"],[119,"to"],[120,"it?"],[121,"No,"],[122,"it"],[123,"does"],[124,"not."]]},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55425/size6/a842841215689dd8bcce4f8d8090eb92.jpg","text":"Does the metal ruler stick to this block?\nPlink, click! Yes, it sticks.","words":[[125,"Does"],[126,"the"],[127,"metal"],[128,"ruler"],[129,"stick"],[130,"to"],[131,"this"],[132,"block?"],[133,"Plink,"],[134,"click!"],[135,"Yes,"],[136,"it"],[137,"sticks."]]},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55426/size6/921648832fadd4b6947e26b50deef831.jpg","text":"Does this hairy brown coconut stick to it?\nNo, it does not.","words":[[138,"Does"],[139,"this"],[140,"hairy"],[141,"brown"],[142,"coconut"],[143,"stick"],[144,"to"],[145,"it?"],[146,"No,"],[147,"it"],[148,"does"],[149,"not."]]},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55441/size6/613e3c3a0a756f6c24ff12a0f6bd1030.jpg","text":"The hairy coconut tickles Rinky’s nose.\nAH-CHOO! She sneezes loudly.\nThe pen flies out of her hand and disappears under the bed.\nRinky is worried. Bhaiya will be back soon!","words":[[150,"The"],[151,"hairy"],[152,"coconut"],[153,"tickles"],[154,"Rinky’s"],[155,"nose."],[156,"AH-CHOO!"],[157,"She"],[158,"sneezes"],[159,"loudly."],[160,"The"],[161,"pen"],[162,"flies"],[163,"out"],[164,"of"],[165,"her"],[166,"hand"],[167,"and"],[168,"disappears"],[169,"under"],[170,"the"],[171,"bed."],[172,"Rinky"],[173,"is"],[174,"worried."],[175,"Bhaiya"],[176,"will"],[177,"be"],[178,"back"],[179,"soon!"]]},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55435/size6/0056d018d95efd075b5aab193b360ed3.jpg","text":"She sticks her hand under the bed.\nOh no! She can’t reach the pen.","words":[[180,"She"],[181,"sticks"],[182,"her"],[183,"hand"],[184,"under"],[185,"the"],[186,"bed."],[187,"Oh"],[188,"no!"],[189,"She"],[190,"can’t"],[191,"reach"],[192,"the"],[193,"pen."]]},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55434/size6/a9ff4da39d4c0e73a5ab1f57400187fd.jpg","text":"She tries to reach the pen with the ruler.\nOh no! The pen slides farther away.\nIf only there was a way to bring the pen closer to her.","words":[[194,"She"],[195,"tries"],[196,"to"],[197,"reach"],[198,"t